
1. install GDB package
yum install gdb

2. Convert program to output file
gcc -g -o output_file program_file.c

3. Open gdb debugger
gdb output_file

4. Play with dugbugging.

i] Add breakpoint
break main
break file_1:fun2

ii] Run Module
run
run "arg1" "arg2"

iii] Continue after Break Point
c

iv] Execute next program line or step over any function calls in the line.
next

v] Execute next program line (after stopping); step into any function calls in the line.
step

vi] Print line
list file_1:fun2
list  // print 10 ine





